data.description: Welcome to the charm and character of this timeless ranch home in the heart of Newport News! Nestled in a quiet neighborhood, this well-maintained property exudes warmth and offers a classic appeal. Retreat to the bedrooms, where the hardwood floors continue to create a timeless and comforting living experience. Venture outside to the large fenced-in backyard, a private oasis where you can enjoy the fresh air and perhaps create your own outdoor haven. This house features new/updated kitchen in 2015, new windows and roof under lifetime warranty in 2019, new HVAC in 2009, and encapsulated crawl in 2013.
